{"tid":1596762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"930柴灣中學生集會","createTime":"2019-09-26T15:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:46:46.000Z","uid":212790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e9c9ab57e5c58255cae6ab98032bd780e0e8da","tid":1596762,"uid":212790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"記住黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmjsFo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmjsFo3.jpg&h=1d7c4270&s={SIZE}\" />經歷了三個多月的抗爭，政府仍然拒絕接受一眾香港人的意見和訴求，漠視民眾的憤怒，令大家忍無可忍。為了讓更多的巿民和學生勇敢發聲，向政府表達強烈的訴求，柴灣區和小西灣區的一眾學生籌辦了柴灣區國殤晚會，希望願意為未來出一分力的各位可以積極參與和支持。活動內容包括自由發言時間、放映會、唱歌等，為令晚會更加有意義，籌辦方亦邀請了區內的幾位區議員到場作分享，敬請期待！活動歡迎所有人參與，包括附近街坊、居民，希望各位踴躍參與，謝謝！<br />\n舉辦日期：9月30日<br />\n活動開始時間：19：00<br />\n舉辦地點：柴灣二號足球場<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！<br />\nFight for freedom ！<br />\nStand with Hong Kong ！"},{"pid":"9cbe38cf0cb6572061cd4282a16625d5851ef44e","tid":1596762,"uid":212790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c15262f627615ebdc0f9509be76d4f42d0ea7768","tid":1596762,"uid":212790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65b82bb1fada91fdf756cb1d5d57736a1c60182e","tid":1596762,"uid":212790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"899968eb7e17d6b778a92dd4c95159c33f108a63","tid":1596762,"uid":212790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:45:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a39fc88bdeaf300abaacb2e96571d997ec9decda","tid":1596762,"uid":212790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21c3f06cf3a5f2f1737f9f23cdb091855ef0b36d","tid":1596762,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T19:28:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13c11b2df71139dec3176c5e53956d4d1ea7fd1c","t